reviewText: Tough...not for those new to yoga but it will PUSH you to want to be as tough!
Love this series, if you do a couple of them it is a very good workout, I am only a beginner for yoga, however have always been athletic and really enjoy this dvd.
The workouts were a bit too short and light for me.

Good instruction.  Most positions are doable for a beginner, but there are a few that are more advanced.  Watch the routines a couple of times to familiarize yourself with them or you will be scrambling between the moves.  Loved the scenery.
I own several Rodney Yee DVDs and love his classes especially the 20 minute ones...thus the reason I bought this one..I do have to say that this one is too quick for me at times
